Description: About tgextelfinder
        -------------------------
        
        tgextelfinder is a Pluggable application for TurboGears2.
        
        Installing
        -------------------------------
        
        tgextelfinder can be installed both from pypi or from bitbucket::
        
            pip install tgextelfinder
        
        should just work for most of the users
        
        Plugging tgextelfinder
        ----------------------------
        
        In your application *config/app_cfg.py* import **plug**::
        
            from tgext.pluggable import plug
        
        Then at the *end of the file* call plug with tgextelfinder::
        
            plug(base_config, 'tgextelfinder')
        
        You will be able to access the plugged application at
        *http://localhost:8080/tgextelfinder*.
        
        Available Hooks
